                    android:layout_width="wrap_content"
                    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
                    android:text="Definition of Economics –Central Economic Problems – Choice of techniques –Production possibility curve – Opportunity Cost-Micro &amp; Macro Economics Meaning of Demand – Utility-Marginal Utility and Law of Diminishing Marginal Utility-Law of demand - Determinants of Demand – Changes in Demand – Market Demand—Demand, forecasting-Meaning of supply-Law of Supply- Changes in Supply-- Market Price Determination – Implications of Government Price Fixation Production function – Law of Variable proportion – Returns to scale – Iso-quants and Isocost line- Least cost combination of inputs – Cost concepts – Private cost and Social Cost - Short run and Long run cost- cost curves – Revenue – Marginal, Average and Total RevenueBreak even Analysis"
